    content: `üö® **Workflow Processing Error v3.0**\n\nA critical error occurred while formatting your response.\n\n**Error**: ${error.message}\n**Time**: ${currentTime}\n\n**Recovery Options**:\n1. Retry your request\n2. Simplify your request\n3. Contact system administrator\n\n**Optimization Status**: v3.0 error handling active`,
